
'''= MetaReciclagem is a self-organized network which proposes the deconstruction of technology for social change.'''

URL = http://rede.metareciclagem.org/


=Description=

The network receives computers and electronics parts, which are used to build computer labs where computer programs are installed with free license to teach society to make better use of the technology, using it for various purposes. It also encourages the use of the internet to create environments that improve the circulation of information.


